{"tid":2495252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨政府：拒簽效忠聲明有8成屬鐵飯碗 包含文職及少數部隊職系","createTime":"2021-04-19T05:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T05:44:15.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7f70476cca091ab9cff84f643051e7390d71ec16","tid":2495252,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"政府稱不理或拒簽聲明公務員中　8成按長期條款聘用<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局局長聶德權表示，按非公務員條款聘任人員簽署聲明的安排，下月將落實和公布。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權出席立法會一個委員會時表示，所有在去年7月1日或之後加入政府的公務員已經簽署聲明，截至今年3月底，涉及約6500名的公務員。至於在去年7月1日前加入政府的公務員，絕大部分簽妥和交回聲明，涉及約17萬人，截至本月1日，共有129名公務員不理會或者拒絕簽妥交回聲明。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權表示，當中8成是按長期聘用條款聘用，約2成是按試用條款聘用，大部分是文職職系人員，少部分是紀律部隊職系人員，他們所屬部門已經去信要求解釋，並已收到部分人的回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586514-20210419.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586514-20210419.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=09d16411\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586514-20210419.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ae221476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586514-20210419.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"79be8b3cbda608b779f60592a9cb1870136f4593","tid":2495252,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"留名睇世界大戰"},{"pid":"9169671de8e3f00e860daf2e3f6f4021cd40da3a","tid":2495252,"uid":133534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}